            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Let's narrow the scope of this PR to only make the few changes internal to vim.pos/vim.range such as https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/39447#discussion_r3148237091 which use number indices *internally*.\r\n\r\nI am writing an outline about next steps (tl;dr, we have multiple confirmations that the perf risk is lower than initially thought, so we can keep the friendly names)",
