        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> because `buf` would be `pos[3]` in a `pos` but `range[5]` in a `range`.\r\n\r\neh... based on `:h getpos()`, it should probably be:\r\n\r\n    [bufnum, lnum, col, off]\r\n\r\nbut... i haven't seen any indication that this matters to anyone, so maybe no one sees this as a problem/confusion.",
            "created_at": "2026-04-27T17:41:00Z",
